*Gdine* sam prošle godine stigao u Srbiju. (I arrived in Serbia last year.)

Prošlog *gdine* sam imao puno posla. (I had a lot of work last year.)

Uživao sam u lepoti *gdine* prošle godine. (I enjoyed the beauty of last year.)

*Gdine* u ovo doba obično padaju snežne padavine. (Snowfall usually occurs at this time of year.)

Jedan od najlepših dana *gdine* bio je kada sam se upoznao sa njom. (One of the best days of the year was when I met her.)